To build bfilter::

    make


To run the test suite::

    make check


To install as a local program, run the following commands from a root
shell, or prefix each command with ``sudo``::

    cp bfilter /usr/local/bin
    cp bfilter.1 /usr/local/share/man/man1


To install as a system program, run the following commands from a root
shell, or prefix each command with ``sudo``::

    cp bfilter /usr/bin
    cp bfilter.1 /usr/share/man/man1


In case of any problems, please contact me via email_ or github_

.. _email: toby@paccrat.org
.. _github: https://github.com/TobyGoodwin/bfilter
